<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v15" title="Q30_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>La fórmula de Euler establece que para cierto tipo de poliedros se cumple la relación entre el número de caras C, aristas A y vértices V dada por la expresión matemática 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>C</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mi>V</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mi>A</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Se comprobó que cierto poliedro que cumple la fórmula de Euler tiene exactamente 12 caras y 8 vértices. Usando la relación anterior, ¿cuántas aristas tiene ese poliedro?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">16<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reemplazar <strong>C = 12</strong> y <strong>V = 8</strong> en la fórmula, se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>. Si <strong>A = 16</strong>, entonces <m:math><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>, y queda <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso, 16 no puede ser el número de aristas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">18<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al reemplazar <strong>C = 12</strong> y <strong>V = 8</strong> en <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, resulta <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, o sea <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>. Restando 2 en ambos lados, se obtiene <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el poliedro tiene 18 aristas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">20<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <strong>C = 12</strong> y <strong>V = 8</strong>, la fórmula queda <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>. Si <strong>A = 20</strong>, entonces <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>, y la igualdad queda <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso, 20 no satisface la relación dada.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">22<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Sustituyendo <strong>C = 12</strong> y <strong>V = 8</strong> en la fórmula, se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, o sea <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>. Si <strong>A = 22</strong>, entonces <m:math><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>, y resulta <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso, 22 no es el número de aristas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso usando la fórmula de Euler</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la relación dada</strong></p>
            <p>La fórmula de Euler para este problema es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar los valores conocidos</strong></p>
            <p>El poliedro tiene 12 caras y 8 vértices, por lo tanto:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Sumar el lado izquierdo</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>20</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces la ecuación queda:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar el número de aristas</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 2 en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>A</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>18</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>A</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El poliedro tiene <strong>18 aristas</strong>, por lo que la alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>